passages.text: This is the final day we will be recording fish. Be sure to submit your catch. [[Tell me more about the fish in Ensomme.]][[Identify and record fish]][[Leave]]

passages.name: Untitled Passage

passages.text: In Ensomme lore, it is said that the ladyfish manifests itself when there is abundant feminity on the island, while the king mackerel represents masculinity.
